  "rationale": "Single sanctioned hero bookend reusing the seeded hero-display-over-staggered-media pattern verbatim: centered didone display title (colossal/display-hero) over two hard-edged photos on the dark inverse surface, gold accent living only on this hero's title, measured copy bound verbatim. The ONE varied axis is aspect-ratio: hero-media keeps width 'media' + z 'mid' (a placed collage image, not a background layer) but now renders as a pano 3:1 strip, and the offset overlap-media reads as a 3:4 portrait crossing the base image's lower edge via the measured registration (bottom edge, depthBaselines 10, z front). Overlap + stagger treatments, spacing, type tiers, and palette are identical to the seed."
